 to break even a pledge that </div><div class="t m5d8 x73 h27 y884 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">has been obtained by fraud, if the performance of </div><div class="t mcfa x74 h27 y882 ff4 fs7 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">it does not involve a direct sin against God. </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
